Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:12.93,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:21.92,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:35.06,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:39.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:44.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:48.98,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:53.54,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:16.00,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.07,0:01:20.53,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:29.41,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:12.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:21.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:35.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:39.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:44.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:48.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:53.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:16.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.07,0:01:20.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:29.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是梦?还是我的幻觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,那是千真万确的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,一切全都是从那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我用塔罗牌算起\N我的恋爱运的那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,100)}命运的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,100)}{\a6}崩坏之塔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,帮我算一下命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,她到底在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,练习已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,下一批!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到,你严重迟到了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们这些选手练习迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挨骂的可是我这个经理耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉,抱歉,因为写报告拖了点时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这些了,男生都已经测完了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的是最后一批!你的目标现在才要登场!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10…10秒64…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳\N好厉害,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长破了11秒耶!太厉害了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来轮到女生了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风好热
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,您准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信您一定可以成功除龙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您兄长的失败就由您…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了,巴尔卡斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绝对不会背对敌人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是再多躺一下子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过幸好并没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑步的姿势越来越漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为你从国中开始就很认真练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直没办法跑低于13秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能跑得像你一样快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题应该在起跑的力道上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇气奋力往前冲出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇气?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的坠子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这个啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我祖母的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它很有趣喔 只要像这样子摆动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就会像钟摆一样\N一秒一次地,一直摆动下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:08:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2,3,4,5,6
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7,8,9,10
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11,12,13
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14,15,16
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎\N17…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳!我帮你把书包…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉!由加莉,我在叫你耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也说句话嘛,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕月堂的草莓麻糬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铄仓屋的起司蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湘南本铺的铜锣烧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义大利传统店的薄荷冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上每天奉上不同的点心 我就放过你这次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是故意昏倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样子的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是我突然目出来碍事\N你早就跟学长大有进展了,对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打你喔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳?\N咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有算过你跟学长的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…要是算出来的结果不好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要是喜欢的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉,你是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,我不小心听到学长他们的聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说学长…天野学长可能会去国外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能连县大会都没办法参加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很明白你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是早点表白吧 不然会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不说一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,小瞳 洗澡水放好了喔 小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩坏之塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表遥远相隔的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长要到国外去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也见不到面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙的A?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇气?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很遗憾没办法跟大家一起参加县大会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们一定会跑出好成绩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在那边等你们的好消息!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长,到了那边以后，请写信给我们喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请千万别忘了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 学长 学长 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我有件事想请你答应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个坠子摆完13下前跑完100公尺的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我低于13秒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你接受我的初吻!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别后悔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎,你准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇气奋力往前冲出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇气!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7…8…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是什么人?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎!\N小瞳!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳!你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男生…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…我在梦里见到的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,同学…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,アブゲーン クァル ェ ジィアボ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弄错了!我们并不是魔界的住民!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要问你是谁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是法尼利亚的梵!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你听得懂他说的话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙也会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩,你快逃吧!地龙要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想被龙吃掉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?这次又是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难过…我好想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是你的对手!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?你不是肚子饿了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吃我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棘手的猎物留到最后对付,是吧!那个女的,你快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!天野学长,往山边去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你扭伤脚了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来背你\N学长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里应该就安全了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎!是!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把剑根本就伤不了它的鳞片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人不会有事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会死掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男生会死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险…上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小伤还用不着你来为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要谢礼是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就到我的城来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,你可别太得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份谢礼只是为了表达\N将你们卷入这场战斗的歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是因为有你的帮助\N让我才能打倒那头龙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在神气什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是以为你会死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为你会死掉…所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕耶!怕得不得了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不会说声谢谢吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道我就不该帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你被龙吃掉算了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球?!为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会看到地球?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里靠近阿萨斯村
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?阿萨斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.11,0:22:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远相隔与“龙的A”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在终于明白其中的真正意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮与地球高挂在天空的奇妙世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:50.96,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就是这颗星球的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:09.71,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:18.16,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:25.79,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:31.94,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:34.30,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:39.31,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:43.15,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:46.95,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:50.96,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:54.46,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的鼓动无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:24:01.93,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带着你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好,跟古书上写的一模一样,可以启动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是艾斯嘉科尼?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.66,0:24:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:09.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:18.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:25.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:31.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:34.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:39.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:43.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:46.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:50.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:54.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:24:01.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい


